gText_Colress_EndofDemo:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: This is the end of the\n"
	.string "demo. Our engineers are still\l"
	.string "working on the remainder of the\l"
	.string "{COLOR RED}Pokémon Battle Labyrinth{COLOR DARK_GREY}.\p"
	.string "Please save your game using the in\n"
	.string "game save so you might be able to\l"
	.string "transfer your save file to the next\l"
	.string "version when it comes out.$"

gText_Colress_RulesReminder:
	.string "You need a reminder of the rules?\n"
	.string "Of course.$"

gText_Colress_Rules:
	.string "The Battle Labyrinth is comprised\n"
	.string "of many {COLOR RED}Zones{COLOR DARK_GREY} you must traverse.\p"
	.string "In these Zones, you might encounter\n"
	.string "wild Pokémon, great treasures,\l"
	.string "tough trainers, and more.\p"
	.string "At the end of each Zone and before\n"
	.string "the next Zone begins, you will find\l"
	.string "a {COLOR RED}Sanctuary{COLOR DARK_GREY}, like this one, with\l"
	.string "shops to purchase supplies, heal\l"
	.string "your Pokémon, and other benefits.\p"
	.string "Once you enter a new Zone, you will\n"
	.string "not be able to access a Sanctuary\l"
	.string "until you exit that Zone.$"

gText_Colress_DontLose:
	.string "You must progress through all Zones\n"
	.string "without losing a battle, which\l"
	.string "would result in an automatic\l"
	.string "reset of the simulation.$"

gText_Colress_ReachedZone:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Congratulations.\n"
	.string "You have cleared {COLOR RED}Zone {STR_VAR_1}{COLOR DARK_GREY}.$"

gText_RewardClear:
	.string "Your reward for clearing {COLOR RED}Zone {STR_VAR_1}{COLOR DARK_GREY} is...$"

gText_Colress_WhenUReady:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: When you are prepared to\n"
	.string "enter {COLOR RED}Zone {STR_VAR_1}{COLOR DARK_GREY}, come speak to me.$"

gText_Colress_Greetings:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Greetings, {PLAYER}.\n"
	.string "What can I help you with?$"

gText_Colress_SureReadyToLeave:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Are you sure you're ready?\n"
	.string "You will be entering {COLOR RED}Zone {STR_VAR_1}{COLOR DARK_GREY}.$"

gText_Colress_Empower:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Bring out the strength of you\n"
	.string "and your Pokémon!$"

gText_Colress_Unlocked:
	.string "Because of your progress,\p"
	.string "the following shops are upgraded:$"

gText_Colress_UnlockedGeneral:
	.string "{COLOR RED}Tim's General Purpose Shop{COLOR DARK_GREY}!$"

gText_Colress_UnlockedUnique:
	.string "{COLOR RED}Silph Unique Item Shop{COLOR DARK_GREY}!$"

gText_Colress_UnlockedServices:
	.string "{COLOR RED}Lelouch's Special Services Shop{COLOR DARK_GREY}!$"

gText_Colress_HeresAPieceofAdvice:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}Here's a piece of advice.$"

gText_Colress_WantMoreAdvice:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Colress{COLOR DARK_GREY}Do you want more advice?$"

gText_Advice0:
	.string "While you are on the Pokémon stats\n"
	.string "screen, you can press the L button\l"
	.string "to show the Pokémon's IVs,\l"
	.string "the R button to show the\l"
	.string "Pokémon's EVs, and the\l"
	.string "Start button to show the\l"
	.string "Pokémon's stats again.$"

gText_Advice1:
	.string "You can press the Start button\n"
	.string "while in the Bag to sort items.$"

gText_Advice2:
	.string "Though it costs money,\n"
	.string "Joy's Healing Shop is often the\l"
	.string "most cost-effective means to heal\l"
	.string "your Pokémon.$"

gText_Advice3:
	.string "Remember to stock up on supplies at\n"
	.string "Tim's General Purpose Shop before\l"
	.string "heading out into the next Zone.\p"
	.string "You do not want to be unable to\n"
	.string "heal your Pokémon.$"

gText_Advice4:
	.string "Antidotes are crucial for curing\n"
	.string "Poison, as your Pokémon can faint\l"
	.string "from it in the overworld.$"

gText_Advice5:
	.string "Defeating other Trainers is the\n"
	.string "best way to make money.\p"
	.string "Try to battle as many as you can so\n"
	.string "you will have money to spend.$"

gText_Advice6:
	.string "Silph Unique Item Shop hosts a huge\n"
	.string "variety of items, but they are\l"
	.string "often overpriced. Make sure to\l"
	.string "spend your money carefully.$"

gText_Advice7:
	.string "Lelouch's Special Services Shop\n"
	.string "is a powerful resource,\l"
	.string "but be sure to use it sparingly.$"

gText_Advice8:
	.string "If you're unsure, you can always\n"
	.string "check the documentation for\l"
	.string "information on nearly everything.$"

gText_Advice9:
	.string "Don't save the game in the middle\n"
	.string "of a Zone. If you find you cannot\l"
	.string "pass through that Zone with your\l"
	.string "current party, you may get\l"
	.string "soft-locked.$"

gText_Advice10:
	.string "It is more advantageous to have a\n"
	.string "full party of well trained Pokémon\l"
	.string "than a few higher leveled Pokémon.$"

gText_GeneralSign:
	.string "Tim's General Purpose Shop\n"
	.string "Sponsored by Pokémart Inc.$"

gText_Tim_Intro:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: New challenger, huh?\n"
	.string "The name's Tim Johnson.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Tim{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I run this store, sponsored by\n"
	.string "Pokémart Incorporated.\l"
	.string "You can find all sorts of general\l"
	.string "supplies for your travels.$"

gText_Tim_Welcome:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Tim{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Welcome to Tim's.\n"
	.string "Can I get you anything?$"

gText_Tim_Leave:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Tim{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Have a nice day.$"

gText_UniqueSign:
	.string "Silph Unique Item Shop\n"
	.string "Need something? We probably got it!$"

gText_Varrick_Intro:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Wowza! Yeetastic! Blamo!\p"
	.string "My name is Varrick,\n"
	.string "entrepreneur extraordinaire!\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I pitched this idea to\n"
	.string "Silph a couple years back,\l"
	.string "and now it's become a reality!\p"
	.string "All the random items you can't find\n"
	.string "in the world, you'll find here!\p"
	.string "Fantastic evolution stones!\p"
	.string "Countless Pokéball variations!\p"
	.string "Delicious Berries!\p"
	.string "The greatest held item collection\n"
	.string "you've never seen!\p"
	.string "Please, enjoy my shop!$"

gText_Varrick_ZhuLiIntro1:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Fantastic! You've arrived!\n"
	.string "Zhu Li, do the thing!$"

gText_ZhuLi_ZhuLiIntro1:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Zhu Li{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Yes, sir.$"

gText_Varrick_ZhuLiIntro2:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Zhu Li is my assistant!\p"
	.string "Silph gave me so many items to sell\n"
	.string "that I practically begged them for\l"
	.string "some extra help!\p"
	.string "Zhu Li, introduce yourself!$"

gText_ZhuLi_ZhuLiIntro2:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Zhu Li{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Yes, sir.\p"
	.string "Pleased to meet you, {PLAYER}. I'm-$"

gText_Varrick_ZhuLiIntro3:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Alright, we don't have all\n"
	.string "day, Zhu Li! Talk to her if you\l"
	.string "want to buy Pokéballs or Evolution\l"
	.string "items, while I'll handle all of the\l"
	.string "other important items!$"

gText_Varrick_Welcome:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Greetings and salutations!\n"
	.string "Welcome to Silph Unique Item Store!$"

gText_Varrick_Leave:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Varrick{COLOR DARK_GREY}: A big thank you from Silph!$"

gText_ZhuLi_Welcome:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Zhu Li{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Welcome to Silph Unique\n"
	.string "Item Store. Care to buy anything?$"

gText_ZhuLi_Leave:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Zhu Li{COLOR DARK_GREY}: We thank you for your\n"
	.string "business, loyal customer.$"

gText_ServicesSign:
	.string "Lelouch's Special Services Shop\n"
	.string "Anything for the right price...$"

gText_Lelouch_Intro1:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: You... What is your name?\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: {PLAYER}? Now that's a name...\n"
	.string "I haven't heard in...$"

gText_Lelouch_Intro2:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: You may call me Lelouch.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I provide a variety of\n"
	.string "services to improve one's Pokémon.$"

gText_Lelouch_NoShards:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I demand a special price\n"
	.string "for my services, one that I see you\l"
	.string "cannot pay. Leave.$"

gText_Lelouch_ExplainShards:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I sense...\n"
	.string "The aura of Shards.\p"
	.string "There are four types of Shards:\n"
	.string "Red, Blue, Yellow, and Green,\l"
	.string "ranked by least to most rare.\p"
	.string "Each can be exchanged for a certain\n"
	.string "type of service I provide.\p"
	.string "Pokémon training costs Red Shards.\p"
	.string "Move Relearning costs Blue Shards.\p"
	.string "Move Tutoring costs Yellow Shards.\p"
	.string "Other services cost Green Shards.\p"
	.string "I hope they serve you well...$"

gText_Lelouch_Welcome:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: For the right price...\n"
	.string "Welcome to Lelouch's Special Services.$"

gText_Lelouch_NotEnoughColor:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: You don't have any Shards\n"
	.string "of that color.$"

gText_Lelouch_CostsRedShards:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Each training session\n"
	.string "costs one Red Shard.$"

gText_Lelouch_Exp1:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Experience Training 1\n"
	.string "costs one Red Shard, are you sure?$"

gText_Lelouch_PayRed:
	.string "{PLAYER} handed over 1 Red Shard.$"

gText_LelouchDefeated:
	.string "Excellent work.\n"
	.string "Your Pokémon have grown stronger.$"

gText_Lelouch_CostsBlueShards:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Move Reminder services\n"
	.string "cost one Blue Shard.\p"
	.string "Would you like me to teach a\n"
	.string "forgotten move to your Pokémon?$"

gText_Lelouch_RemindWhichMon:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Which Pokémon should\n"
	.string "relearn a move?$"

gText_Lelouch_RemindWhichMove:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Which move should it\n"
	.string "relearn?$"

gText_Lelouch_CantRemindMon:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: That Pokémon cannot\n"
	.string "relearn any moves.$"

gText_Lelouch_PayBlue:
	.string "{PLAYER} handed over 1 Blue Shard.$"

gText_Lelouch_CantRemindEgg:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: That is an Egg.$"

gText_Lelouch_Leave:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Lelouch{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Farewell.$"

gText_HealingSign:
	.string "Joy's Healing Shop\n"
	.string "Health care costs money!$"

gText_Joy_CantUse:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: You can't use that without paying!$"

gText_Joy_Intro:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Welcome to the Pokémon…\n"
	.string "Ugh. Never mind.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}???{COLOR DARK_GREY}: My name is Joy. Just Joy.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: I used to work at the\n"
	.string "Pokémon Center, but they gave\l"
	.string "terrible pay.\p"
	.string "So I've started my own shop,\n"
	.string "Joy's Healing Shop!$"

gText_Joy_Welcome:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Welcome to Joy's Healing Shop.\p"
	.string "We heal your Pokemon for a flat\n"
	.string "¥500 fee, which also comes with\l"
	.string "complimentary access to the PC.$"

gText_Joy_Nuzlocke:
	.string "I will also remove any fallen\n"
	.string "Pokémon in your party.$"

gText_Joy_WouldYouLikeToHeal:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Should I heal your Pokémon?$"

gText_Joy_NotEnough:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: You don't have enough money.$"

gText_Joy_ThankYou:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: That will be ¥500, thank you…$"

gText_Joy_PartyHealed:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Your party has been restored.\n"
	.string "You also now have access to the PC.$"

gText_Joy_WonderfulDay:
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}Joy{COLOR DARK_GREY}: Have a wonderful day!$"

gText_ExitSign:
	.string "This is the exit!\n"
	.string "If you leave, you can't come back.$"

gText_NotEnoughMons:
	.string "You need at least two Pokémon to\n"
	.string "initiate a Double Battle.$"
